\layout Title

Companies Report
\layout Author

Paul Brannan
\layout Abstract

Three companies were compared for qualities which may be important in considerin
g a job later in life.
 The three companies compared include Healthcare.com, Not a Number, and the
 Automated Trading Desk.
 I am most familiar with Healthcare.com, and Not a Number does work which
 is in my primary field of interest.
 ATD also does interesting work, and brings in extraordinary revenues, and
 can therefore provide the best benefits to its employees.
 Of the three companies, ATD seems to be the best company to work for.
\layout Standard


